 store takh\u00f8yde for sp\u00f8ker"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|kuriosa"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "7caf3f5a1a06e9f99bb5a5244ebd4d724a42500606773340f7a984af37f94712"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T23:39:34.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Er julenissen en karateekspert? Det er ikke alltid enkelt for guidene \u00e5 holde maska."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1371192.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/museumgullkorn"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a1c9dc3f4c0325d16fb111e22c1ab7f7d8730377.jpg?5907c736"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Barnas gullkorn p\u00e5 museum -adressa.no", "Kunsten \u00e5 assosiere", "For en arbeidsplass!", "Levende stein", "Drager og p\u00f8lser", "Rumpe p\u00e5 utstilling"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "a1c9dc3f4c0325d16fb111e22c1ab7f7d8730377"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "kuriosa"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["jente", "museum", "barn", "fullt alvor", "elev", "barnas gullkorn", "lita jente", "historie", "formidler"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["victoria", "aktivitetsleder martin kulhawczuk", "petter", "egge museum", "vitensenteret", "\u00e5rets", "lita", "ringve", "kongens", "vitenskapsmuseet"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["steinkjer", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["gunhild rikstad", "ann siri hegseth garberg", "gunnar holt", "claudia b\u00e4tcke"]}, {"